official_title: Human Papillomavirus Ends Here: A Multilevel Intervention to Increase Uptake of the HPV Vaccine Among Adolescents
inclusion_criteria:
• Clinic patients between the ages of 10-12 who are eligible for the HPV vaccine
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 10 Years
Must have maximum age of 12 Years
exclusion_criteria: • Clinic patients who already received the HPV vaccine or with any contraindication to the HPV vaccine.
